  8.Css properties for the following
  a)aligning text horizontally
   h1 {
     text-align: left;
   }

  h1 {
    text-align: right;
  }

  b)aligning text vertically

   h1 {
     text-align: center;
   }

   C)Transforming to uppercase/lowercase

   h1 {
    text-tarnsform: uppercase;
   }

   h1 {
     text-transform: lowercase;

   }

   D) Adding strike into text.

   <p><s>My house is red.</s></p>